{{Infobox cricketer | name = Dawlat Ahmadzai | image = | country = Afghanistan | fullname = Dawlat Khan Ahmadzi | birth_date = {{Birth date and age|1984|11|5|df=yes}} | birth_place = [[Logar Province]], [[Afghanistan]] | heightft = | heightinch = | batting = Right-handed | bowling = Right-arm [[seam bowling|fast-medium]] | role = | international = true | testdebutdate = | testdebutyear = | testdebutagainst = | testcap = | lasttestdate = | lasttestyear = | lasttestagainst = | odidebutdate = 19 April | odidebutyear = 2009 | odidebutagainst = Scotland | odicap = | oneodi = | lastodidate = 16 February | lastodiyear = 2010 | lastodiagainst = Canada | odishirt = | IT20debutdate = 1 February | IT20debutyear = 2010 | IT20debutagainst = Ireland | IT20cap = | oneIT20 = true | lastIT20date = 1 February | lastIT20year = 2010 | lastIT20against = Ireland | IT20shirt = | club1 = | year1 = | club2 = | year2 = | clubnumber1 = | deliveries = balls | columns = 4 | column1 = [[One Day International|ODI]] | matches1 = 3 | runs1 = &ndash; | bat avg1 = &ndash; | 100s/50s1 = &ndash;/&ndash; | top score1 = &ndash; | deliveries1 = 112 | wickets1 = 1 | bowl avg1 = 121.00 | fivefor1 = &ndash; | tenfor1 = &ndash; | best bowling1 = 1/40 | catches/stumpings1 = &ndash;/&ndash; | column2 = [[Twenty20 International|T20I]] | matches2 = 2 | runs2 = 2 | bat avg2 = &ndash; | 100s/50s2 = &ndash;/&ndash; | top score2 = 2[[not out|*]] | deliveries2 = 24 | wickets2 = 1 | bowl avg2 = 23.00 | fivefor2 = &ndash; | tenfor2 = &ndash; | best bowling2 = 1/21 | catches/stumpings2 = &ndash;/&ndash; | column3 = [[First-class cricket|FC]] | matches3 = 2 | runs3 = 13 | bat avg3 = 13.00 | 100s/50s3 = &ndash;/&ndash; | top score3 = 7[[not out|*]] | deliveries3 = 244 | wickets3 = 9 | bowl avg3 = 15.33 | fivefor3 = 1 | tenfor3 = &ndash; | best bowling3 = 5/52 | catches/stumpings3 = &ndash;/&ndash; | column4 = [[List A cricket|LA]] | matches4 = 9 | runs4 = 34 | bat avg4 = 34.00 | 100s/50s4 = &ndash;/&ndash; | top score4 = 11[[not out|*]] | deliveries4 = 388 | wickets4 = 2 | bowl avg4 = 174 | fivefor4 = &ndash; | tenfor4 = &ndash; | best bowling4 = 1/5 | catches/stumpings4 = &ndash;/&ndash; | date = 25 February | year = 2010 | source = http://www.cricinfo.com/ci/content/player/25917.html Cricinfo }}
'''Dawlat Ahmadzai''' (born September 5, 1984) is a right-handed batsman and right arm [[Seam bowling|fast-medium]] bowler who plays for [[Afghanistan national cricket team|Afghanistan]].
After the Afghan team secured [[One Day International]] status by securing a top-six finish at the [[2009 ICC World Cup Qualifier]] in South Africa (although not qualifying for the [[2011 Cricket World Cup]] itself), on April 19, 2009 he took the first ever wicket for Afghanistan in an ODI when he dismissed [[Scotland national cricket team|Scotland]]'s [[Gavin Hamilton (cricketer)|Gavin Hamilton]] as the Afghan team won the Qualifier's fifth-place play-off at [[Willowmoore Park]], [[Benoni, Gauteng|Benoni]].<ref> {{cite web |url=https://cricketarchive.com/Archive/Scorecards/211/211269.html |title=Afghanistan v Scotland in 2008/09 |accessdate=April 19, 2009 |publisher=CricketArchive}}</ref>
